You ARE permitted to:

a) View, read, and study the source code for personal or educational purposes.

b) Use the Software to convert, port, or migrate mods/assets that you personally authored or have explicit written permission to modify.

c) Fork and Modify: Create public or private forks of the Software on hosting platforms (e.g., GitHub, GitLab).

d) Distribute Modifications: Redistribute modified versions of the source code only if the purpose is to submit improvements to the original Software via Pull Request or to provide a community patch that requires the original Software to function.

e) Contribute to the Software via pull requests, subject to acceptance by Indozilla1234.

