2. PROHIBITED USES (THE "STRICT" CLAUSES)

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

You ARE NOT permitted to:

a) Hard Forking & Fragmentation: You may not redistribute the Software or its derivatives as a separate, competing product. Any public fork must remain downstream of the original repository and may not be rebranded or marketed as a replacement for ModMorpher.

b) Unauthorized Conversion: Use the Software to convert any mod or asset for which you do not hold explicit permission.

c) Circumvention: Bypass any DRM or access control associated with Minecraft: Bedrock Edition or the Minecraft Marketplace.

d) Commercialization: Redistribute, resell, or commercially exploit the Software (or its forks) without explicit written permission from Indozilla1234.

e) Trademark & Attribution: Remove or alter the "ModMorpher" name, copyright notices, or this license. You may not use the name "ModMorpher" for any modified version in a way that suggests it is the official version.

f) Standalone Redistribution: You may not host a "compiled" (.exe, .jar, etc.) version of a fork for public download if it is intended to bypass the official distribution channels.

